BREAKING: Pharmaceutical giant Pfizer is ready to seek U.S. approval for its COVID-19 vaccine "within days".

The company says a final analysis of clinical trial data shows its shot is 95% effective. 

Last week, the early results had suggested 90% efficacy.

More to come. https://t.co/HEAQGrowjC
